title: Rattlesnake Hill (Delaware County, New York)
text: Rattlesnake Hill is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> located in the <a href="Catskill%20Mountains">Catskill Mountains</a> of <a href="New%20York%20%28state%29">New York</a> southeast of <a href="Hancock%20%28village%29%2C%20New%20York">Hancock</a>. <a href="Jensen%20Hill">Jensen Hill</a> is located south, <a href="Bouchoux%20Hill">Bouchoux Hill</a> is located southwest, <a href="Big%20Fork%20Mountain">Big Fork Mountain</a> is located northeast, and <a href="Johnny%20Ridge">Johnny Ridge</a> is located north-northwest of Rattlesnake Hill.
